As soon as you grab the bag from the ground you can feel a tingly warmth within it.
You pull out an amulet of some kind.
It has a bright yellow stone in the middle.
Its name comes to your mind.
It's hard to believe it, even harder to imagine leaving it here.

- Take the Sun Idol.
