It's a list of random things. 
"the dark, the cold, losing you"
It stuns you for a second.
It is a heart ache from ages ago.
A relationship that didn't work.
It's why you are going to this cabin.
To make it right.
You know who's waiting for you there.
You know tomorrow will be too late.
You have already broken your promise.
